WEBVTT

00:00.840 --> 00:01.840
Chen Wan'er

00:02.320 --> 00:03.840
If you want to die, don't drag me with you

00:07.720 --> 00:08.320
Prince of Jin

00:08.480 --> 00:09.960
Found Prince of Jin

00:13.200 --> 00:13.960
Father

00:14.200 --> 00:14.920
Your son never thought

00:14.920 --> 00:16.840
To do such an absurd thing

00:17.440 --> 00:18.080
Father

00:18.720 --> 00:20.080
Our Sikong family's face

00:20.080 --> 00:21.440
Has been completely shamed by you

00:21.920 --> 00:23.720
Now you say you didn't mean it

00:23.720 --> 00:26.120
I'll kick you to death, you worthless thing

00:26.840 --> 00:27.320
Father

00:27.840 --> 00:29.440
Even if you gave your son a hundred times more courage

00:29.720 --> 00:31.840
Your son would never actively do such a foolish thing

00:31.960 --> 00:32.840
Get away

00:34.040 --> 00:34.720
Tomorrow

00:34.920 --> 00:35.560
No

00:35.960 --> 00:37.600
Pack your things today

00:37.600 --> 00:38.840
Go to the southern frontier

00:39.240 --> 00:40.440
Without my edict

00:40.720 --> 00:42.320
You may not leave even one step

00:44.360 --> 00:44.960
Yes
